MediaWiki allows us to define custom templates, which can then be included in other wiki pages. When creating a new one, please add it below, and use the "[[Template:Template]]" at the top of the new template. Check existing templates for reference.

== Available templates ==
* [[Template:alpine|alpine]] ''link to a page on the [https://wiki.alpinelinux.org/ Alpine Wiki]''
* [[Template:albug|albug]] ''link to a bug over at https://bugs.alpinelinux.org/''
* [[Template:button|button]] ''Visual representation for a button or sequence of buttons''
* [[Template:File|file]] ''gitlab or github file link''
* [[Template:github|github]] ''github issue or pull-request link'' (obsolete for postmarketOS code, use [[Template:issue|issue]] or [[Template:MR|MR]] instead)
* [[Template:Hc|hc]] ''block code with header (can be used for listing the contents of a file, with the file location on top)''
* [[Template:Infobox|infobox]] ''on the top right of every device / user interface article''
** [[Template:Infobox_interface|interface]]
** [[Template:Infobox_device|device]]
** [[Template:Infobox_soc|soc]]
* [[Template:issue|issue]] ''gitlab issue link''
* [[Template:MR|MR]] ''gitlab merge request link''
* [[Template:maemo-leste|maemo-leste]] ''[https://github.com/maemo-leste/bugtracker Maemo Leste] bugtracker link''
* [[Template:Mainpage-button|mainpage-button]] ''fancy buttons with icons used on the [[Main Page]]''
* [[Template:milestone|milestone]] ''GitLab [https://gitlab.com/groups/postmarketOS/-/milestones milestone] link''
* [[Template:Note|note]]
* [[Template:Note-device-milestone-main|note-device-milestone-main]] ''WIP for [[Device_categorization|main device category]] with milestone link''
* [[Template:Outdated|outdated]]
* [[Template:Syslog|syslog]] ''short explanation on how to read relevant syslog entries''
* [[Template:Todo|todo]]
* [[Template:Userbox|userbox]] ''userbox template''
* [[Template:wikipedia|wikipedia]] ''link to an wikipedia article''

Templates for device ownership list:
* [[Template:My devices|My devices]] ''Show table of devices owned on your own page''
* [[Template:Owns device|Owns device]] ''Adds a device to the ownership table''
* [[Template:Device owners|Device owners]] ''Displays list of people owning the device to the device page''

Userboxes:
* [[Template:User_ports]] ''Shows the amount of devices you ported'' (usage: {<p style="display:inline;"></p>{User ports|amount}})
* [[Template:User_mainline]] ''Shows the amount of devices you mainlined'' (usage: {<p style="display:inline;"></p>{User mainline|amount}})
* [[Template:User_mainline_attempts]] ''"This user is currently trying to mainline a device."''

